Lipid lowering and anti-ageing effects of edible flowers of Viola x wittrockiana 
Gams in a Caenorhabditis elegans obese model.

Núñez S(1), López V(1)(2), Moliner C(1), Valero MS(2)(3), Gómez-Rincón C(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Pharmacy, Faculty of Health Sciences, Universidad San Jorge, 
